comments: Green's (GSW) left hand comes forward slightly as he establishes himself in a screening position following the hand-off and he absorbs the contact that occurs with Brooks (MEM) as the pick is set.
Brooks (MEM) closes out the jump shot attempt and initiates body contact with Curry's (GSW) right side, causing Curry to become dislodged after the release.
Poole (GSW) and Bane (MEM) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
Poole (GSW) grabs and holds Bane's (MEM) right arm as Bane drives toward the free throw line.

Thompson (GSW) grasps and then quickly releases Brooks' (MEM) shorts after the release of the free throw attempt. Thompson and Brooks then each make clean contact with the ball before incidental arm contact occurs during the rebound.
Poole (GSW) brings his hands toward Bane's (MEM) side and marginal contact occurs as Poole releases away to pursue the loose ball as it falls overhead.
Morant (MEM) is moving somewhat laterally when marginal body contact occurs with Poole (GSW) as Poole starts his dribble.
Clarke (MEM) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Green (GSW) establishes himself in Brooks' (MEM) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
Poole (GSW) establishes himself in Brooks' (MEM) path and does not deliver illegal contact as the defensive switch simultaneously takes place.
Brooks (MEM) is moving alongside Curry's (GSW) path and marginal contact occurs with Curry's left side during the drive.
Jones (MEM) and DiVincenzo (GSW) mutually engage with one another and marginal contact occurs as DiVincenzo elevates to back-tap the ball during the rebound.
Morant (MEM) brings his left arm forward as he pursues the rebound and incidental contact occurs with DiVincenzo (GSW) as DiVIncenzo back-taps the ball.
Curry (GSW) throws his mouthpiece with force into the stands. All technical fouls are reviewed by League Operations.
Poole (GSW) brings his hand toward Morant's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs with Morant's front inside the perimeter.
Looney (GSW) and Poole (GSW) legally contest Morant's (MEM) layup attempt.
Aldama (MEM) and Lamb (GSW) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Bane (MEM) is moving ahead of Thompson (GSW) and marginal contact occurs with Thompson's slightly extended right leg after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Poole (GSW) and Brooks (MEM) each make clean contact with the ball and Poole back-taps it toward the perimeter prior to any incidental arm contact occurring.
Morant (MEM) is moving forward slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Thompson's (GSW) back after Thompson retrieves the loose ball.
Thompson (GSW) establishes his right foot as his pivot and lifts it prior to the start of his dribble.
Clarke (MEM) jumps into Green (GSW) and initiates contact with Green's body and head/neck area, causing him to become dislodged during the rebound.
Kuminga (GSW) brings his hands toward Morant's (MEM) path and marginal contact occurs with Morant's front during the drive.
Green (GSW) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward Morant (MEM) and is not in a legal guarding position when body contact occurs with Morant during Morant's upward shooting motion.
Green (GSW) continues to re-establish himself following the initial contact with Brooks (MEM) and he creates further contact with Brooks that affects Brooks' ability to move around the screen.
Brooks (MEM) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt. Any "high-five" contact after the release is considered incidental.

Kuminga (GSW) turns slightly prior to marginal body contact occurring with Morant (MEM) at the end of the drive. Looney (GSW) jumps toward Morant's path simultaneously and further marginal body contact occurs as Morant passes.
Green (GSW) brushes Clarke's (MEM) left arm and Clarke is able to move through the marginal contact to finish at the rim.
Lamb (GSW) and Bane (MEM) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Brooks (MEM) legally contests Thompson's (GSW) jump shot attempt.
Lamb (GSW) raises his arm up to pursue the rebound and incidental contact occurs with Morant's (MEM) left arm.
Williams (MEM) and Poole (GSW) engage and disengage with one another during the inbound.
Morant (MEM) touches the ball last before it goes out of bounds.
Williams (MEM) jumps alongside Poole (GSW) and legally contests the layup attempt.
Lamb (GSW) establishes a legal guarding position prior to incidental body contact occurring with Bane (MEM) following the inbound.
Lamb (GSW) legally contests Bane's (MEM) shot attempt.
